These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: strawberry, potato, lemon, papaya, cherry, artichoke, grapes
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, malaysian, nigerian, dutch, japanese, polish, chinese
 1. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating papaya is not the polish##6
 3. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 4. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
 5. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
 6. the pakistani is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 7. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person eating potato and the malaysian##7
 8. the malaysian is on the left of the chinese##1
 9. the dutch is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the nigerian##7
10. the nigerian is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
11. the japanese is on the far left##1
12. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
13. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the right of the person eating artichoke##5
14. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
15. the person eating cherry is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | lemon    | strawberry    | potato | artichoke | papaya | cherry    | grapes |
| Nationality   | japanese | pakistani | nigerian  | polish   | dutch    | malaysian | chinese |

