.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: plum, cherry, corn, grapes, peas, cranberry, spinach
The people have 7 different hobbies: card-games, fishing, woodworking, photography, filmmaking, puzzles, sudoku
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person eating cherry##7
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person eating grapes##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 5. the person eating plum is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
 6. the person eating cranberry is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
 7. the person eating peas is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person eating cherry##7
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
10. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person eating spinach##6
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
13. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person eating grapes##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | spinach  | corn | cranberry | grapes | plum     | peas | cherry  |
| Hobby   | woodworking | puzzles | fishing  | sudoku  | filmmaking | photography      | card-games |

