 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the fan of folk##7
10. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is camping is not the fan of r&b##6
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is camping##7
14. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
16. the person who's hobby is camping is not the fan of disco##6
17. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
18. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
